# myweb

This is the source code for my personal website: **[willdevbrook.onrender.com](https://willdevbrook.onrender.com/)**

## Hey, I'm Will 👋

I make whatever I feel like making.  
Games, tools, websites, experiments — if it seemed like a good idea at the time, it's probably somewhere on here.

No strict theme, no posting schedule, just whatever sparks joy (or curiosity) at the moment.

### What you'll find on the site
- **Small tools and experiments** you can actually play with (starting with a calculator that has a **banana mode** 🍌)
- A **side-scrolling shooter** written entirely in vanilla JavaScript — one file, 1000+ lines, zero regrets
- Random projects, half-baked ideas, and whatever else I felt like building

Basically: the serious ones and the ridiculous ones, all living together in harmony.

## Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- Vanilla JavaScript

No frameworks, no build tools, no nonsense. Just plain web stuff because that's what I felt like using.

## Why this repo exists
It's the home for the code behind my little corner of the internet. Feel free to poke around, take inspiration, or straight-up steal bits if you find something useful (just don't forget to have fun with it).

## Want to see the site?
→ **[willdevbrook.onrender.com](https://willdevbrook.onrender.com/)**

Made with whatever mood I was in at the time.  
Come say hi if you like weird little projects.

